reviewText: The last four cds didn't work.  The labels were poorly installed and would not allow them to play in multiple cd players.  The material was great.  I wish I could have listened to all of the CDs.
3 of the 10 CD's in the set were unplayable. Made me very upset. Should never have bought from this vendor.

If you are in sales this is a MUST for you!!  The approaches are known in the sales community but usually carry a different label.  However, Tony gives you the recipe for doing it in the right order and gives you example (role playing) to make it real.  I have been through other selling strategy classes and never got as much as I did from this set of tapes.  To me, it is worth every cent!
